Interface ServerInfoAwareProviderFactory<T extends Provider>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ProviderFactory<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    JpaConnectionProviderFactory, MongoConnectionProviderFactory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultJpaConnectionProviderFactory, DefaultMongoConnectionFactoryProvider

    public interface ServerInfoAwareProviderFactory<T extends Provider>
extends ProviderFactory<T>
    Marker interface for ProviderFactory of Provider which wants to show some info on "Server Info" page in Admin console.
    Author:
    Vlastimil Elias (velias at redhat dot com)

      • getOperationalInfo

        Map<String,String> getOperationalInfo()
        Get operational info about given provider. This info contains informations about providers configuration and operational conditions (eg. errors in connection to remote systems etc) which is shown on "Server Info" page.
        Returns:
        Map with keys describing value and relevant values itself
